        "title": "Blank field, java causing app crash",
        "body": "<p>When the field is left blank it makes the app crash. How can i stop it ?<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>EditText editText = (EditText)findViewById(R.id.editText);\nuserNumber = Integer.parseInt(editText.getText().toString());\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I tried giving it a .setError(\"Don't leave this blank!\"), but it doesn't seem to do the thing, the app crashes there.<\/p>\n\n<p>Screenshots:<br>\n     <a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/z9Ckqm.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/JwQXKl.png\" alt=\"screen-shot\"><\/a>\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/z9Ckqm.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/z9Ckqm.png\" alt=\"error-message\"><\/a><\/p>\n",
