            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1456318291,
            "creation_date": 1456318291,
            "body": "<p>This code can give you an idea,<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String input = editText.getText().toString();\nif(input.length() &gt; 0){\n    try {\n        int userNumber = Integer.parseInt(input);\n\n        // Write your code here\n\n    } catch (Exception e) {\n        Toast.makeText(this, \"Enter only a number!\", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n        e.printStackTrace();\n    }\n} else{\n    Toast.makeText(this, \"Enter a number!\", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
